For the listing of various ship manufacturers and points of sale for these ships, please consult [[Ship Manufacturers]]. For general information about ships, see [[Ships]].

__TOC__

== Column legend ==

{| class="wikitable" style="margin:0;"
! Code !! Meaning
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:left;" | Identity
|-
| <code>Ships</code> || Ship name and image
|-
| <code>Manufacturer</code> || Builder — see [[Ship Manufacturers]]
|-
| <code>Crew</code> || Crew officers supported
|-
| <code>Aux</code> || Auxiliary slot type and size, if present
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:left;" | Durability <small>(modifiers ×; blank = baseline 1.0)</small>
|-
| <code>Hull</code> || Hull HP modifier — see [[Stat scaling]]
|-
| <code>Armr</code> || Armor HP modifier — see [[Stat scaling]]
|-
| <code>Shld</code> || Shield HP modifier — see [[Stat scaling]]
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:left;" | Mobility
|-
| <code>Crgo</code> || Cargo capacity
|-
| <code>Spd</code> || Max warp speed <small>(ls/s)</small> — ×7 during [[Navigation#Travel speed|Fast-Lane Travel]]
|-
| <code>Acc</code> || Warp acceleration <small>(ls/s²)</small>
|-
| <code>Tonn</code> || Ship weight in tons
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:left;" | Combat
|-
| <code>Hrdp</code> || Hardpoint slots, size-coded (e.g. 2M 3S)
|-
! colspan="2" style="text-align:left;" | Requirements <small>(— = not available from a shipyard)</small>
|-
| <code>ShpR</code> || Shipyard reputation required
|-
| <code>Cnq</code> || Conquest rank required
|-
| <code>PlyrL</code> || Player level required
|-
| <code>ShpL</code> || Shipyard level required
|}


